472
00:30:41,559 --> 00:30:43,189
<i>Yool dan aku...</i>

473
00:30:49,300 --> 00:30:51,400
<i>...kembali ke Korea
diam-diam...</i>

474
00:30:51,400 --> 00:30:53,300
<i>...dan memulai hidup baru.</i>

475
00:30:56,209 --> 00:30:58,269
Ayah, aku terlambat!

476
00:30:58,840 --> 00:31:00,840
Iya. Ayah hampir selesai.

477
00:31:02,249 --> 00:31:04,780
Kau tak ke sekolah.
Kenapa buru-buru?

478
00:31:04,849 --> 00:31:07,450
Paman Young Cheol
pernah berkata,...

479
00:31:07,680 --> 00:31:09,889
"Gadis cantik datang..."

480
00:31:10,019 --> 00:31:12,760
"...ke taman hiburan
di pagi hari."

481
00:31:13,220 --> 00:31:16,789
Ya ampun. Dia mengajarimu
hal-hal yang tidak berguna.

482
00:31:17,760 --> 00:31:21,729
Biar Ayah lihat
apa anak ayah tampan hari ini.

483
00:31:21,729 --> 00:31:24,970
Aku selalu tampan.

484
00:31:25,130 --> 00:31:27,700
Bagus. Ayah akan keluar
sebentar setelah bersiap-siap.

485
00:31:27,700 --> 00:31:29,169
