486
00:31:39,749 --> 00:31:41,419
Sudah waktunya dia bangun.

487
00:31:51,229 --> 00:31:52,229
Borg Mom!

488
00:31:56,369 --> 00:31:58,630
Kau sungguh mau aku melakukannya?

489
00:32:00,340 --> 00:32:01,340
Ya.

490
00:32:02,410 --> 00:32:03,610
Kau ternyata...

491
00:32:04,639 --> 00:32:06,079
...tidak memercayaiku.

492
00:32:06,079 --> 00:32:09,550
Tidak, aku tak percaya diriku.

493
00:32:18,119 --> 00:32:19,119
